The Company may disclose your Personal Data in good faith that such action is necessary to:
Comply with a legal obligation.
Protection and defense of the rights or property of the Company.
Prevent or investigate potential wrongdoing in connection with the Service.
Protection of the personal safety of Users of the Service or the public.
Protection against legal liability.
